19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c9a44ea106f62b7dcbb0c1db51de5d5752a26f","tid":2340750,"uid":230791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T18:19:56.000Z","msg":"以後見一個中醫屌一個"},{"pid":"0e7c54379d8bd4328eb0c34133aa8437977b71ef","tid":2340750,"uid":104035,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T18:25:18.000Z","msg":"有D病連西醫都要CHECK好耐先確診到<br />\n但中醫撚居然覺得把下脈就check到, 仲要有人信, 真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c229c7f7c63bf5d4b065b399cb6162004f15090d","tid":2340750,"uid":230791,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e7c54379d8bd4328eb0c34133aa8437977b71ef","tid":2340750,"uid":104035,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T18:25:18.000Z","msg":"有D病連西醫都要CHECK好耐先確診到<br />\n但中醫撚居然覺得把下脈就check到, 仲要有人信, 真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T18:27:54.000Z","msg":"中醫撚永遠活係自己世界"},{"pid":"7529c59118f5d4f9fc58d5107806c56d89000adb","tid":2340750,"uid":359029,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T19:06:21.000Z","msg":"中醫藥可能唔夠 Scientific base... 但係針炙可以吧... 無錯經絡是在解剖學上看不見，找不到。<br />\n但是中醫體系入面遠自扁鵲已經用針炙，雖然肯定有水份：但畢竟可以肯定的是即使外國人，也可以去witness, 首推紐約時報記者亦曾經在紐時頭版說出他的肯定針炙上的療效，至於是否安慰劑，我相信在人類的歷史上自有公論。<br />\n世衞也承認針炙有效。<br />\nJohn Hopkin 夠照吧，參見<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.hopkinsmedicine.org/health/wellness-and-prevention/acupuncture\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hopkinsmedicine.org%2Fhealth%2Fwellness-and-prevention%2Facupuncture&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nv